solution:
解 在导体中， $\boldsymbol{j}=\sigma \boldsymbol{E}, \rho=0$，故麦克斯韦方程组为

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}=-\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{B}}{\partial t}, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}=\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{D}}{\partial t}+\boldsymbol{j} \\
& \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{D}=\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0 \\
& \boldsymbol{D}=\varepsilon \boldsymbol{E}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}=\mu \boldsymbol{H}
\end{aligned}
$$

对于定态电磁波

$$
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)=\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)=\boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t}
$$

由麦克斯韦方程组可得

\begin{gather*}
\left\{\begin{array}{l}
\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=\mathrm{i} \omega \mu \boldsymbol{H}(\boldsymbol{x}) \\
\nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}(\boldsymbol{x})=-\mathrm{i} \omega \varepsilon \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})+\sigma \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x}) \\
\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{x})=0
\end{array}\right.  \tag{1}\\
\begin{aligned}
\nabla \times(\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E})=\nabla(\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E})-\nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E}=-\nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E} \\
\quad=\mathrm{i} \omega \mu \nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}=\left(\omega^{2} \varepsilon \mu+\mathrm{i} \omega \mu \sigma\right) \boldsymbol{E}
\end{aligned}
\end{gather*}

令

\begin{equation*}
k^{\prime 2}=\omega^{2} \mu \varepsilon^{\prime}, \quad \varepsilon^{\prime}=\varepsilon+\mathrm{i} \frac{\sigma}{\omega} \tag{2}
\end{equation*}

则

\begin{equation*}
\nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})+k^{\prime 2} \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=0 \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

这是亥姆霍兹方程，平面波是其一种特解。即

$$
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=\boldsymbol{E}_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{k}^{\prime} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}}
$$

$\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}$ 为复波矢量. 令 $\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}=\boldsymbol{\beta}+\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{\alpha}$，则有

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \beta^{2}-\alpha^{2}=\omega^{2} \mu \varepsilon \\
& \boldsymbol{\beta} \cdot \boldsymbol{\alpha}=\frac{1}{2} \omega \mu \sigma
\end{aligned}
$$

对本题，入射波 $E=E_{y 0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k z-\omega t)}$，且

$$
\boldsymbol{k}=k \boldsymbol{e}_{z}, \quad \boldsymbol{E}_{0}=\boldsymbol{E}_{y 0} \boldsymbol{e}_{y}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}_{0}=\boldsymbol{B}_{x 0} \boldsymbol{e}_{x}
$$

设在半无限介质中的透射波为 $\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime \prime} 、 \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime \prime}$，有

$$
\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime \prime}=\boldsymbol{E}_{0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\left(k^{\prime} \cdot z-\omega t\right)}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime \prime}=\boldsymbol{B}_{0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\left(k^{\prime} \cdot z-\omega t\right)}
$$

在分界面上，为保证面上各点的边值关系都成立，必须要求

$$
\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}=\left.\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}\right|_{z=0}
$$

从而可得

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \alpha_{x}=\alpha_{y}=\beta_{x}=\beta_{y}=0 \\
& \boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}=k^{\prime} \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \\
& k^{\prime}=\beta+\mathrm{i} \alpha
\end{aligned}
$$

$\beta$ 、 $\alpha$ 满足联立方程

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \beta^{2}-\alpha^{2}=\omega^{2} \mu \varepsilon \\
& \beta \alpha=\frac{1}{2} \omega \mu \sigma
\end{aligned}
$$

其解为

\begin{align*}
& \beta=\omega \sqrt{\mu \varepsilon}\left[\frac{1}{2}\left(1+\sqrt{1+\frac{\sigma^{2}}{\varepsilon^{2} \omega^{2}}}\right)\right]^{1 / 2}  \tag{4}\\
& \alpha=\omega \sqrt{\mu \varepsilon}\left[\frac{1}{2}\left(-1+\sqrt{1+\frac{\sigma^{2}}{\varepsilon^{2} \omega^{2}}}\right)\right]^{1 / 2} \tag{5}
\end{align*}

下面用边值关系求透射波的振幅。设反射波的振幅为 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}^{\prime} 、 \boldsymbol{H}_{0}^{\prime}$ ，由平面波的横波性及在分界面上 $\boldsymbol{E}$ 的法向连续性及 $\boldsymbol{H}$ 的切向连续性，首先可知反射波与折射波的电场只有 $y$ 分量，磁场只有 $x$ 分量，并且满足

\begin{align*}
& E_{y 0}+E_{y 0}^{\prime}=E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}  \tag{6}\\
& E_{x 0}+E_{x 0}^{\prime}=E_{x 0}^{\prime \prime} \tag{7}
\end{align*}

对入射波与反射波 $H_{x 0}=\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon_{0}}{\mu_{0}}} E_{y 0}, H_{x 0}^{\prime}=\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon_{0}}{\mu_{0}}} E_{y 0}^{\prime}$ 。并由式(1)得 $H_{x 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{k^{\prime}}{\omega \mu} E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}$ ，从而可把式（7）化成

\begin{equation*}
\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon_{0}}{\mu_{0}}}\left(E_{y 0}-E_{y 0}^{\prime}\right)=\frac{k^{\prime}}{\omega \mu} E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime} \tag{8}
\end{equation*}

式(6)与式(8)联立，解得

\begin{equation*}
E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{1+\sqrt{\frac{\mu_{0}}{\varepsilon_{0}}} \cdot \frac{k^{\prime}}{\omega \mu}} \tag{9}
\end{equation*}

当 $\sigma$ 很大且为实数， $\omega$ 是低频时，有

$$
\frac{\sigma}{\varepsilon \omega} \gg 1, \quad \sqrt{1+\frac{\sigma^{2}}{\varepsilon^{2} \omega^{2}}} \pm 1 \approx \frac{\sigma}{\varepsilon \omega}
$$

所以

\begin{equation*}
\beta=\alpha \approx \sqrt{\frac{\omega \mu \sigma}{2}} \tag{10}
\end{equation*}

故

\begin{align*}
& k^{\prime}=\sqrt{\frac{\omega \mu \sigma}{2}}(1+\mathrm{i}) \\
& E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{\left(1+\sqrt{\frac{\mu_{0} \sigma}{2 \varepsilon_{0} \omega \mu}}+\mathrm{i} \sqrt{\frac{\mu_{0} \sigma}{2 \varepsilon_{0} \omega \mu}}\right)} \tag{11}
\end{align*}

即在金属中的电场为

\begin{equation*}
E^{\prime \prime}=E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{-\alpha z} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(\beta z-\omega t)} e_{y} \tag{12}
\end{equation*}

由题意得到 $\boldsymbol{B}$ 和 $\boldsymbol{E}$ 的表达式

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{B}=\nabla \times \boldsymbol{A}=i \boldsymbol{k} \times \boldsymbol{A}_{0} e^{i(\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}-\omega t)} \\
& \boldsymbol{E}=-\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{A}}{\partial t}=i \omega \boldsymbol{A}_{0} e^{i(\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}-\omega t)}
\end{aligned}
$$

(c) 由 $\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E}=0$，得到 $\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{A}_{0}=0$。

由 \(\boldsymbol{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0\)，有
\[
\begin{array}{ll}
\text{在 } x=0, a \text{ 面,} & H_{x}=0 \\
\text{在 } y=0, b \text{ 面,} & H_{y}=0 \tag{5}
\end{array}
\]

将式(3)应用到边界面上，并考虑到 \(\boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{E}=0\)，有
\[
\begin{array}{lll}
\text{在 } x=0, a \text{ 面,} & \frac{\partial H_{z}}{\partial x}=0, & \frac{\partial H_{y}}{\partial x}=\frac{\partial H_{x}}{\partial y} \\
\text{在 } y=0, b \text{ 面,} & \frac{\partial H_{z}}{\partial y}=0, & \frac{\partial H_{y}}{\partial x}=\frac{\partial H_{x}}{\partial y} \tag{6}
\end{array}
\]

令 $\bar{W}(t) = \frac{1}{2} W_{0}$，则有

$$
\begin{gathered}
e^{-\frac{e^{2} \omega_{0}^{2}}{6 \pi \varepsilon_{0} m c^{3}} \tau} = \frac{1}{2}, \quad \frac{e^{2} \omega_{0}^{2}}{12 \pi \varepsilon_{0} m c^{3}} \tau = \ln 2 \\
\tau = \frac{12 \pi \varepsilon_{0} m c^{3}}{e^{2} \omega_{0}^{2}} \ln 2 = 1.1 \times 10^{-7} \, \mathrm{s}
\end{gathered}
$$

answers:
\boxed{\boldsymbol{E}= 
\begin{cases}
\frac{q r}{2 \pi \varepsilon_{0} R^{2} l}, & r<R \\
\frac{q}{2 \pi \varepsilon_{0} r l}, & r>R
\end{cases}}

solution:
(c) 空间反射变换为

$$
\begin{array}{ll}
\boldsymbol{r} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{r}^{\prime} = -\boldsymbol{r}, & \nabla \rightarrow \nabla^{\prime} = -\nabla \\
\frac{\partial}{\partial t} \rightarrow \frac{\partial}{\partial t^{\prime}}, & e \rightarrow e^{\prime} = e
\end{array}
$$

显然此时有

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \rho(\boldsymbol{r}, t) \rightarrow \rho^{\prime}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = \rho, \\
& \boldsymbol{j} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{j}^{\prime} = -\boldsymbol{j}
\end{aligned}
$$

由电荷守恒定律，再写出变换后不变形的麦克斯韦方程，仿（b）做法，可证明

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = -\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{r}, t), \\
& \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = \boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)
\end{aligned}
$$

设带电粒子在 $\mathrm{d} t$ 时间内的位移为 $\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x}$，则引起矢势 $\boldsymbol{A}$ 的增量为 $(\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \cdot \nabla) \boldsymbol{A}$，因此 $\boldsymbol{A}$ 的变化率为

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{A}}{\mathrm{~d} t}=\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{A}}{\partial t}+(\boldsymbol{v} \cdot \nabla) \boldsymbol{A} \tag{1}
\end{equation*}

在电磁场中动量为 $\boldsymbol{P}$ 的带电粒子的运动方程为

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{P}}{\mathrm{~d} t}=e(\boldsymbol{E}+ \boldsymbol{v} \times \boldsymbol{B}) \tag{2}
\end{equation*}

注意在拉格朗日形式中，$x$ 与 $\boldsymbol{v}$ 是独立变量，故有

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{v} \times (\nabla \times \boldsymbol{A})=\nabla(\boldsymbol{v} \cdot \boldsymbol{A})-(\boldsymbol{v} \cdot \nabla) \boldsymbol{A} \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

式(3)代入式(2), 本题中 $\varphi=0$，即得

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{P}}{\mathrm{~d} t}=e \nabla(\boldsymbol{v} \cdot \boldsymbol{A})-e \frac{\mathrm{~d} \boldsymbol{A}}{\mathrm{~d} t} \tag{4}
\end{equation*}

本题的平面电磁波矢势 $\boldsymbol{A}(x-c t)$ 与坐标 $y 、 z$ 无关，因此 $\nabla(\boldsymbol{v} \cdot \boldsymbol{A})$ 没有横向分量。对横向分量 $\boldsymbol{P}_{\perp}=P_{y} \boldsymbol{e}_{y}+P_{z} \boldsymbol{e}_{z}$，运动方程为

\begin{equation*}
\frac{\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{P}_{\perp}}{\mathrm{d} t}=-e \frac{\mathrm{~d} \boldsymbol{A}_{\perp}}{\mathrm{d} t} \tag{5}
\end{equation*}

对式（5）积分得

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{P}_{\perp}=-e \boldsymbol{A}_{\perp}+C \tag{6}
\end{equation*}

由于粒子初速为 0，故常数 $C$ 等于零。且由 (a)，有 $A_{z}=0, \boldsymbol{A}_{\perp}=\boldsymbol{A}$。所以最后得到

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{P}_{\perp}=-e \boldsymbol{A} \tag{7}
\end{equation*}

\[
\begin{aligned}
w &=\frac{1}{2}\left(\varepsilon_{0} E^{2}+\frac{1}{\mu_{0}} B^{2}\right) \\
&= 
\begin{cases}
\left(1+\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}\right) \frac{q^{2} r^{2}}{8 \pi^{2} \varepsilon_{0} R^{4} l^{2}}, & r<R \\
\left(1+\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}\right) \frac{q^{2}}{8 \pi^{2} \varepsilon_{0} r^{2} l^{2}}, & r>R
\end{cases}
\end{aligned}
\]

电子的电量与质量的大小为

$$
e=-1.6 \times 10^{-19}\text{C}, \quad m=9.1 \times 10^{-31}\text{kg}
$$

另有 $\varepsilon_{0}=8.85 \times 10^{-12} \mathrm{~F} / \mathrm{m}$.\\
对于电离层 $N=10^{12}/\mathrm{m}^{3}$，有

$$
\begin{aligned}
\omega_{\mathrm{p}} & =\sqrt{\frac{N e^{2}}{m \varepsilon_0}}=\left[\frac{10^{6} \times 10^{6} \times\left(1.6 \times 10^{-19}\right)^{2}}{9.1 \times 10^{-31} \times 8.85 \times 10^{-12}}\right]^{\frac{1}{2}} \\
& \approx 5.64 \times 10^{7}\text{Hz}
\end{aligned}
$$

对于金属钠，$N=2.5 \times 10^{28}/\mathrm{m}^{3}$，有

$$
\begin{aligned}
\omega_{\mathrm{p}} & =\left[\frac{2.5 \times 10^{28} \times 10^{6} \times\left(1.6 \times 10^{-19}\right)^{2}}{9.1 \times 10^{-31} \times 8.85 \times 10^{-12}}\right]^{\frac{1}{2}} \\
& \approx 8.91 \times 10^{15}\text{Hz}
\end{aligned}
$$

麦克斯韦方程为

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{D}=0, \quad \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0 \\
& \nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}=-\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{B}}{\partial t}, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{B}=\mu_{0} \frac{\partial \boldsymbol{D}}{\partial t} \\
& \boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{D}=\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0 \\
& \boldsymbol{k} \times \boldsymbol{B}=-\omega \boldsymbol{D}, \quad \boldsymbol{k} \times \boldsymbol{E}=\omega \boldsymbol{B}
\end{aligned}
$$

于是

$$
\boldsymbol{k} \times(\boldsymbol{k} \times \boldsymbol{E})=\boldsymbol{k}(\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{E})-\boldsymbol{k}^{2} \boldsymbol{E}=-\mu_{0} \omega^{2} \boldsymbol{D}
$$

有

$$
\left(k^{2}-\frac{\omega^{2}}{v^{2}}\right) \boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{k}(\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{E})-\mathrm{i} \mu_{0} \omega^{2}(\boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{g})=0
$$

写成分量方程：

\begin{align*}
& \left(k^{2}-\frac{\omega^{2}}{v^{2}}\right) E_{x}-\mathrm{i} \mu_{0} \omega^{2} g E_{y}=0 \tag{1} \\
& \mathrm{i} \mu_{0} \omega^{2} g E_{x}+\left(k^{2}-\frac{\omega^{2}}{v^{2}}\right) E_{y}=0 \tag{2}
\end{align*}

其中, $v=\frac{1}{\sqrt{\mu_{0} \varepsilon}}$。

\begin{equation*}
\varepsilon E_{z}=0 \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

由式（3）可知，$E_{z}=0$，故为横波。\\
由式（1）、式（2），有非零解条件要求

$$
\operatorname{det}\begin{vmatrix}
k^{2}-\frac{\omega^{2}}{v^{2}} & -\mathrm{i} \mu_{0} \omega^{2} g \\
\mathrm{i} \mu_{0} \omega^{2} g & k^{2}-\frac{\omega^{2}}{v^{2}}
\end{vmatrix}=0
$$

可求得如下色散关系

$$
k^{2}=\frac{\omega^{2}}{v^{2}} \pm \mu_{0} \omega^{2} g
$$

折射指数有两种取值：

$$
N_{1}=\frac{c k_{+}}{\omega}=\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon}{\varepsilon_{0}}+\frac{g}{\varepsilon_{0}}}, \quad N_{2}=\frac{c k_{-}}{\omega}=\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon}{\varepsilon_{0}}-\frac{g}{\varepsilon_{0}}}
$$

problem:
考虑自由空间中下列形式的电磁波

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} kz - \mathrm{i} \omega t}, \\
& \boldsymbol{B}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} kz - \mathrm{i} \omega t}
\end{aligned}
$$

(b) 在理想导体表面处, $\boldsymbol{E}$ 和 $\boldsymbol{B}$ 的边界条件是什么？

solution:
平均辐射功率为

\[
\begin{aligned}
P & = \int \frac{\mathrm{d} P}{\mathrm{~d} \Omega} \mathrm{~d} \Omega = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{4} a^{4} i_{0}^{2}}{32 c^{3}} \cdot 2 \pi \int_{0}^{\pi} \sin^{3} \theta \mathrm{~d} \theta \\
& = \frac{\pi \mu_{0} \omega^{4} a^{4} i_{0}^{2}}{12 c^{3}}
\end{aligned}
\]

从而得散射场为（利用 $a \ll \lambda$ 的条件）

$$
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{B} & =\frac{e^{i K R}}{4 \pi \varepsilon_{0} c^{3} R} \ddot{\boldsymbol{P}} \times \boldsymbol{e}_{R}=\frac{(\varepsilon-\varepsilon_{0}) a^{3} \omega^{2}}{(\varepsilon+2 \varepsilon_{0}) c^{2} R} E_{0} \sin \theta e^{i(K R-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi} \\
\boldsymbol{E} & =c \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{n}=c \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{e}_{R} \\
& =\frac{(\varepsilon-\varepsilon_{0}) a^{3} \omega^{2}}{(\varepsilon+2 \varepsilon_{0}) c^{2} R} \boldsymbol{E}_{0} \sin \theta e^{i(K R-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}
\end{aligned}
$$

类似地，要使 $\boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} = 0$，由

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} = \gamma\left(\boldsymbol{B} - \frac{\boldsymbol{v}}{c^{2}} \times \boldsymbol{E}\right)
\end{equation*}

知，这时要求

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{B} = \frac{\boldsymbol{v}}{c^{2}} \times \boldsymbol{E}
\end{equation*}

另外，由

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B} = \frac{1}{c^{2}} \boldsymbol{E} \times (\boldsymbol{v} \times \boldsymbol{E}) = \frac{E^{2}}{c^{2}} \boldsymbol{v}
\end{equation*}

可以看出, 只要取 $\boldsymbol{v} = \frac{c^{2}}{E^{2}} \boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B}$, 即可使 $\boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} = 0$。而电场为

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} = \gamma(\boldsymbol{E} + \boldsymbol{v} \times \boldsymbol{B}) = \gamma\left(1 - \frac{c^{2} B^{2}}{E^{2}}\right) \boldsymbol{E} = \frac{\boldsymbol{E}}{\gamma} \neq 0
\end{equation*}

另外

\begin{equation*}
\frac{1}{\gamma^{2}} = 1 - \frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}} = 1 - \frac{c^{2} B^{2}}{E^{2}}>0
\end{equation*}

综合上述, 当 $E^{2} > c^{2} B^{2}$ 时, 且取 $\boldsymbol{v} = \frac{c^{2}}{E^{2}}(\boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B})$, 将有 $\boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} = 0, \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} \neq 0$。

依题意，在实验室系 $\Sigma$ 中，束流的电荷密度为 $\rho$，由于洛伦兹纵向收缩效应，知在束流的静系 $\Sigma^{\prime}$ 中，电荷密度为 $\rho / \gamma (\gamma = \frac{1}{\sqrt{1 - v^{2}/c^{2}}})$。在 $\Sigma^{\prime}$ 系中， $\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} = \frac{\rho r^{\prime}}{2 \varepsilon_{0} \gamma} \boldsymbol{e}_{r}, \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} = 0$。在实验室系 $\Sigma$ 中， $v = v e_{z}$，所以

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}_{\perp} = \gamma (\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} - v \times \boldsymbol{B})_{\perp} = \gamma \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime}, \quad \boldsymbol{E}_{\parallel} = \boldsymbol{E}_{\parallel}^{\prime} = 0 \\
& \boldsymbol{B}_{\perp} = \gamma (\boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} + \frac{v}{c^{2}} \times \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime})_{\perp} = \gamma \frac{v}{c^{2}} \times \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}_{\parallel} = \boldsymbol{B}_{\parallel}^{\prime} = 0
\end{aligned}
$$

故电子受力为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{F} & = -e \boldsymbol{E} - e v \times \boldsymbol{B} = -e \cdot \gamma \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} - e v \times \left(\gamma \frac{v}{c^{2}} \times \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} \right) \\
& = -e \gamma \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} + e \gamma \frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}} \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime}
\end{aligned}
$$

由于横向无洛伦兹收缩， $r = r^{\prime}$，所以

$$
\boldsymbol{F} = -\frac{e \boldsymbol{E}^{\prime}}{\gamma} = -\frac{e \rho r}{2 \varepsilon_{0} \gamma^{2}} \boldsymbol{e}_{r}
$$

answers:
\[
\boxed{\boldsymbol{B} = -\frac{\varepsilon-\varepsilon_{0}}{\varepsilon+2\varepsilon_{0}} \cdot \frac{\omega^{2} a^{3}}{c^{3} r} E_{0} e^{i(k r-\omega t)} \sin \theta \boldsymbol{e}_{\phi}, \boldsymbol{E} = -\frac{\varepsilon-\varepsilon_{0}}{\varepsilon+2\varepsilon_{0}} \cdot \frac{\omega^{2} a^{3}}{c^{2} r} E_{0} e^{i(k r-\omega t)} \sin \theta \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}}
\]

solution:
介质情况下的麦克斯韦方程组是

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{D}=0, \quad \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0 \\
& \nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}=-\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{B}}{\partial t}, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}=\boldsymbol{J}+\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{D}}{\partial t}
\end{aligned}
$$

注意这里的场 $\boldsymbol{E}$、$\boldsymbol{B}$ 是外来场和随时间变化的磁化强度 $\boldsymbol{M}(t)$ 产生的场的叠加，即已经包含了 $\boldsymbol{M}(t)$ 产生的场。

由于是绝缘介质，并假定介质无法带电，即有 $\rho=0, \quad \boldsymbol{J}=0$。又因 $\varepsilon_{r}=1$，有 $\boldsymbol{D}=\varepsilon_{0} \boldsymbol{E}$。故方程简化为

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E}=0, \quad \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0 \\
& \nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}=-\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{B}}{\partial t}, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}=\varepsilon_{0} \frac{\partial \boldsymbol{E}}{\partial t}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}=\mu \boldsymbol{H}
\end{aligned}
$$

并由此导出波动方程为

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E}-\mu \varepsilon_{0} \frac{\partial^{2} \boldsymbol{E}}{\partial t^{2}}=0 \\
& \nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{H}-\mu \varepsilon_{0} \frac{\partial^{2} \boldsymbol{H}}{\partial t^{2}}=0
\end{aligned}
$$

此方程的平面波特解为

$$
\boldsymbol{H}(t)=\boldsymbol{H}_{0} e^{i(kz-\omega t)}
$$

将其代入波动方程，可得色散关系为

$$
k^{2}-\mu \varepsilon_{0} \omega^{2}=0, \quad k^{2}=\frac{\omega}{v_{p}}=\omega \sqrt{\mu(\omega) \varepsilon_{0}}=\frac{\omega}{c} \sqrt{\mu(\omega)}
$$

介质的磁化强度平面波为

$$
\boldsymbol{M}(t)=\chi_{m}(\omega) \boldsymbol{H}(t)=\chi_{m} \boldsymbol{H}_{0} e^{i(kz-\omega t)}
$$

故该平面波的色散关系仍然为

$$
k^{2}=\frac{\omega}{v_{p}}=\frac{\omega}{c} \sqrt{\mu(\omega)}
$$

\[
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{g} &=\varepsilon_{0} \boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B} \\
&= 
\begin{cases}
\frac{v q^{2} r^{2}}{4 \pi^{2} \varepsilon_{0} c^{2} R^{4} l^{2}} \boldsymbol{e}_{x}, & r<R \\
\frac{v q^{2}}{4 \pi^{2} \varepsilon_{0} c^{2} r^{2} l^{2}} \boldsymbol{e}_{x}, & r>R
\end{cases}
\end{aligned}
\]

解 辐射平均能流

\begin{equation*}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} = \frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}} |\boldsymbol{B}|^{2} \boldsymbol{e}_{r} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{4} q^{2} a^{2}}{32 \pi^{2} c^{2} r^{2}}\left(1 + \cos^{2} \theta\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{r} \tag{4}
\end{equation*}

平均辐射功率

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{P} = \oint \overline{\boldsymbol{S}} \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{r} r^{2} \mathrm{~d} \Omega = \frac{\mu_{0} q^{2} a^{2} \omega^{4}}{6 \pi c} \tag{5}
\end{equation*}

$\boldsymbol{E}_{0}=E_{0} \boldsymbol{e}_{x}$，而

$$
e_{\mathrm{r}} \times e_{x}=\cos \theta \cos \phi e_{\mathrm{r}}-\sin \phi e_{\theta}
$$

辐射光强即辐射平均能流密度，为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} & =\frac{1}{2} \operatorname{Re}\left\{\boldsymbol{E}^{*} \times \boldsymbol{H}\right\} \\
& =\frac{1}{2 \mu_{0}} \operatorname{Re}\left\{-c\left(\boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \times \boldsymbol{B}^{*}\right) \times \boldsymbol{B}\right\}
\end{aligned}
$$

由题图 5.4 知，$e_{\mathrm{r}} \cdot \boldsymbol{B}_{0}=0$，故得

$$
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}}=\frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}}|\boldsymbol{B}|^{2} \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}=\frac{\mu_{0} q^{4} E_{0}^{2}}{32 \pi^{2} c m^{2} r^{2}}\left(\cos ^{2} \theta \cos ^{2} \phi+\sin ^{2} \phi\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}
$$

解 由题意，在 $\Sigma$ 系内，$\boldsymbol{E} \perp \boldsymbol{B}$，且 $v // \boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B}$，故有 $\boldsymbol{E} \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0, \boldsymbol{E}_{//}=\boldsymbol{B}_{//}=0$。由场的变化关系知，在 $\Sigma^{\prime}$ 系内场量为

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{E}_{//}^{\prime} = \boldsymbol{E}_{//}, \quad \boldsymbol{E}_{\perp}^{\prime} = \gamma(\boldsymbol{E} + \boldsymbol{v} \times \boldsymbol{B})_{\perp}
\end{equation*}

式中, $\gamma = \frac{1}{\sqrt{1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}}}$。由式知, 要使 $\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} = 0$, 则要求 $\boldsymbol{E} = \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{v}$。再由

$$
\boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B} = (\boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{v}) \times \boldsymbol{B} = B^{2} \boldsymbol{v} - (\boldsymbol{B} \cdot \boldsymbol{v}) \boldsymbol{B} = B^{2} \boldsymbol{v}
$$

知，只要速度取如下形式

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{v} = \frac{\boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B}}{\boldsymbol{B}^{2}}
\end{equation*}

即可使 $\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} = 0$。此时磁场为

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} = \gamma\left(\boldsymbol{B} - \frac{\boldsymbol{v}}{c^{2}} \times \boldsymbol{E}\right) = \gamma\left(1 - \frac{E^{2}}{c^{2} B^{2}}\right) = \frac{\boldsymbol{B}}{\gamma} \neq 0
\end{equation*}

另外

\begin{equation*}
\frac{1}{\gamma^{2}} = 1 - \frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}} = 1 - \frac{(E \times B)^{2}}{c^{2} B^{4}} = \frac{c^{2} B^{2} - E^{2}}{c^{2} B^{2}}>0
\end{equation*}

综合上述, 当 $c^{2} B^{2} > E^{2}$, 且取 $v = \frac{\boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B}}{B^{2}}$, 则有 $\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime} = 0, \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime} \neq 0$。

answers:
\[
\boxed{\frac{\omega^{4} a^{2} E_{0}^{2} \sin ^{2} \theta}{32 \pi^{2} \varepsilon_{0} c^{3} r^{2}} \cdot \frac{\sin ^{2}\left[\frac{1}{2} N k a(1-\sin \theta \cos \phi)\right]}{\sin ^{2}\left[\frac{1}{2} k a(1-\sin \theta \cos \phi)\right]}}
\]

solution:
平均能流密度为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} & = \frac{1}{\mu_{0}} \overline{\operatorname{Re} \boldsymbol{E} \times \operatorname{Re} \boldsymbol{B}} \\
& = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{6} q^{2} z_{0}^{4} \sin^{2} \theta \cos^{2} \theta}{16 \pi^{2} c^{3} r^{2}} \overline{\sin^{2}(2 \omega t)} \boldsymbol{n}
\end{aligned}
$$

而

$$
\overline{\sin^{2}(2 \omega t)} = \frac{1}{T} \int_{0}^{T} \sin^{2}(2 \omega t) \mathrm{d} t = \frac{1}{2}
$$

故

$$
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{6} q^{2} z_{0}^{4} \sin^{2} \theta \cos^{2} \theta}{32 \pi^{2} c^{3} r^{2}} \boldsymbol{n}
$$

单位立体角的辐射功率为

$$
\frac{\mathrm{d} P}{\mathrm{d} \Omega} = \overline{\boldsymbol{S}} \cdot \boldsymbol{n} r^{2} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{6} q^{2} z_{0}^{4} \sin^{2} \theta \cos^{2} \theta}{32 \pi^{2} c^{3}}
$$

problem:
考虑自由空间中下列形式的电磁波

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} kz - \mathrm{i} \omega t}, \\
& \boldsymbol{B}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} kz - \mathrm{i} \omega t}
\end{aligned}
$$

其中，$\boldsymbol{E}_{0}$ 和 $\boldsymbol{B}_{0}$ 在 $xy$ 平面内。

(a) 求 $k$ 和 $\omega$ 之间的关系及 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y)$ 和 $\boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y)$ 之间的关系。证明 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y)$ 和 $\boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y)$ 满足自由空间中静电学和静磁学方程。

solution:
(a) 求 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y)$ 和 $\boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y)$ 的关系，自然应该用麦克斯韦方程中以下两式：

$$
\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E} = -\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{B}}{\partial t}, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{B} = \frac{1}{c^{2}} \cdot \frac{\partial \boldsymbol{E}}{\partial t}
$$

将所给电磁波形式

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(kz - \omega t)}, \\
& \boldsymbol{B}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(kz - \omega t)}
\end{aligned}
$$

代入上述两式即有

\begin{align*}
& \mathrm{i} k \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) = \mathrm{i} \omega \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) - \nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0} \tag{1}\\
& \mathrm{i} k \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) = -\mathrm{i} \frac{\omega}{c^{2}} \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) - \nabla \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0} \tag{2}
\end{align*}

由于 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}$ 、 $\boldsymbol{B}_{0}$ 在 $xy$ 平面上，可证明 $\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0}$ 和 $\nabla \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}$ 只有 $z$ 方向上的分量，而 $\boldsymbol{e}_{z} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0}$ 及 $\boldsymbol{e}_{z} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}$ 都在 $xy$ 面内，由式（1）、式(2)可知，只能

\begin{equation*}
\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0} = 0, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0} = 0 \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

及

\begin{align*}
& \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) = \frac{\omega}{k} \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) \tag{4}\\
& \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) = -\frac{\omega}{k c^{2}} \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) \tag{5}
\end{align*}

用 $\boldsymbol{e}_{z}$ 叉乘式(4)，再将式(5)代入，即可知

\begin{equation*}
k = \frac{\omega}{c} \tag{6}
\end{equation*}

由式(4)、式(5)可知 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}$ 、 $\boldsymbol{B}_{0}$ 、 $\boldsymbol{e}_{z}$ 三者互相正交且构成右手关系，且有

\begin{equation*}
|\boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y)| = \frac{\omega}{k}|\boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y)| = c|\boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y)| \tag{7}
\end{equation*}

又由麦克斯韦方程 $\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E} = 0, \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B} = 0$ 可得

\begin{equation*}
\boldsymbol{\nabla} \cdot \boldsymbol{E}_{0} = 0, \quad \boldsymbol{\nabla} \cdot \boldsymbol{B}_{0} = 0 \tag{8}
\end{equation*}

从式(3)、式(8)知 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y)$ 、$\boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y)$ 满足自由空间中静电磁学方程.

answers:
\[
\boxed{\frac{\mathrm{i} \omega^{2} P_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)}}{2 \pi \varepsilon_{0} c^{3} r} \sin \theta \sin \left(\frac{k}{2} a \sin \theta \cos \varphi\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi}}
\]

solution:
(c) 为求圆偏光折射率 $n_{\pm}$, 首先应求极化率。为此，先求介质中电子的运动。电子运动方程为

$$
m \ddot{\boldsymbol{r}} = -e \boldsymbol{E} - e \dot{\boldsymbol{r}} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}
$$

解的形式为

$$
\boldsymbol{r} = \boldsymbol{r}_{0} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t}
$$

故

$$
-m \omega^{2} \boldsymbol{r} = -e \boldsymbol{E} - e (-\mathrm{i} \omega) \boldsymbol{r} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}
$$

注意 $\boldsymbol{P} = -n_{0} e \boldsymbol{r}$ ，由上式可得

$$
m \omega^{2} \boldsymbol{P} = -n_{0} e^{2} \boldsymbol{E} - \mathrm{i} \omega e \boldsymbol{P} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}
$$

又由 $\boldsymbol{P} = \chi \varepsilon_{0} \boldsymbol{E}$ ，所以

$$
m \omega^{2} \chi \varepsilon_{0} \boldsymbol{E} + n_{0} e^{2} \boldsymbol{E} = -\mathrm{i} \omega e \chi \varepsilon_{0} \boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{0}
$$

令 $\omega_{P}^{2} = \frac{n_{0} e^{2}}{m \varepsilon_{0}}, \; \omega_{B} = \frac{e B_{0}}{m}$, 则

$$
\chi \frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}} \boldsymbol{E} + \boldsymbol{E} = -\mathrm{i} \chi \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}} \boldsymbol{E} \times \boldsymbol{e}_{z}
$$

或

\begin{align*}
& \left(1 + \chi \frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}}\right) E_{x} + \mathrm{i} \chi \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}} E_{y} = 0  \tag{1} \\
& \left(1 + \chi \frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}}\right) E_{y} - \mathrm{i} \chi \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}} E_{x} = 0 \tag{2}
\end{align*}

式 (1)+i 式 (2) 得

\begin{equation*}
\left(1 + \chi \frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}}\right) \left(E_{x} + \mathrm{i} E_{y}\right) + \chi \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}} \left(E_{x} + \mathrm{i} E_{y}\right) = 0 \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

式 (1)-i 式 (2) 得

\begin{equation*}
\left(1 + \chi \frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}}\right) \left(E_{x} - \mathrm{i} E_{y}\right) - \chi \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}} \left(E_{x} - \mathrm{i} E_{y}\right) = 0 \tag{4}
\end{equation*}

因此, 对波模 $E_{x} + \mathrm{i} E_{y}$ (右旋光模式)，由 (3) ，$\chi = \chi_{+}$ 满足

$$
\left(1 + \chi_{+} \frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}}\right) + \chi_{+} \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}} = 0
$$

即

$$
\chi_{+} = -\frac{1}{\frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}} + \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}}}
$$

同样，有

$$
\chi_{-} = \frac{1}{\frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}} - \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}}}
$$

而 $n_{\pm} = \sqrt{\varepsilon_{\pm}} = \sqrt{1 + \chi_{\pm}}$, 故有

$$
\begin{aligned}
& n_{\pm} = \sqrt{1 - \frac{1}{\frac{\omega^{2}}{\omega_{P}^{2}} \pm \frac{\omega}{\omega_{B}}}} = \sqrt{1 - \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega^{2} \pm \frac{\omega \omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega_{B}}}} = \sqrt{1 - \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega\left(\omega \pm \omega_{B}^{\prime}\right)}} \\
& \omega_{B}^{\prime} = \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega_{B}} = \frac{n_{0} e^{2}}{m \varepsilon_{0}} \cdot \frac{\varepsilon_{0} B_{0}}{n_{0} e} = \frac{B_{0} e}{m}
\end{aligned}
$$

当 $\omega \gg \omega_{P}$ 及 $\omega \gg \omega_{B}^{\prime}$ 时

$$
n_{\pm} \approx \sqrt{1 - \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}} \pm \frac{\omega_{P}^{2} \omega_{B}^{\prime}}{2 \omega^{3}} \frac{1}{\sqrt{1 - \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}}} = n \pm \beta
$$

其中

$$
n = \sqrt{1 - \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}}, \quad \beta = \frac{\omega_{P}^{2} \omega_{B}^{\prime}}{2 \omega^{3}} \cdot \frac{1}{\sqrt{1 - \frac{\omega_{P}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}}}
$$

高频指的是 $\omega \gg \omega_{P}$ 及 $\omega \gg \omega_{B}^{\prime}$.

problem:
无限空间中充满不均匀介质，其极化率和电导率分别由下式描述 $(\chi_{\infty}, \lambda, \sigma_{\infty}$ 为常数）

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \chi(z)= \begin{cases}0, & -\infty<z<0 \\ \chi_{\infty}\left(1-\mathrm{e}^{-\lambda z}\right), & 0<z<\infty\end{cases} \\
& \sigma(z)= \begin{cases}0, & -\infty<z \leqslant 0 \\ \sigma_{\infty}\left(1-\mathrm{e}^{-\lambda z}\right), & 0<z<\infty\end{cases}
\end{aligned}
$$

令空间中 $\mu = 1$; 一束 $\mathbf{S}$ 偏振的平面波 (即 $\boldsymbol{E}$ 垂直于入射面) 以入射角 $\theta$ 从 $z<0$ 的区域入射到 $z>0$ 的区域。波矢为 $k_{0},\left(k_{0} c=\omega\right)$

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}_{y}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)=A \exp \left[\mathrm{i}\left(k_{0} \sin \theta \cdot x+k_{0} \cos \theta \cdot z-\omega t\right)\right] e_{y} \\
& \boldsymbol{E}_{y}^{\mathrm{R}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)=R \exp \left[\mathrm{i}\left(k_{0} \sin \theta \cdot x-k_{0} \cos \theta \cdot z-\omega t\right)\right] e_{y} \\
& \boldsymbol{E}_{y}^{\mathrm{T}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)=E(z) \exp \left[\mathrm{i}\left(k^{\prime} \sin \gamma \cdot x-\omega t\right)\right] e_{y}
\end{aligned}
$$

$A, R$ 为入射和反射振幅，$E(z)$ 为待定函数。$\gamma$ 为 $z=0$ 的面法向与 $k^{\prime}$ 的夹角。

(b) 写出各分量在 $z=0$ 处的边界条件(提示：利用斯涅尔定律)。

solution:
(b) 在 $z=0$ 面, $\boldsymbol{E}_{t}, \boldsymbol{H}_{t}$ 连续, 即

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}_{y}^{\mathrm{I}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)+\boldsymbol{E}_{y}^{\mathrm{R}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)=\boldsymbol{E}_{y}^{\mathrm{T}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t), \quad z=0 \\
& \left[\boldsymbol{H}^{\mathrm{I}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)+\boldsymbol{H}^{\mathrm{R}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)\right] \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{x}=\boldsymbol{H}^{\mathrm{T}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{x}, \quad z=0
\end{aligned}
$$

还有 $B_{n}$ 连续，即 $\left[\boldsymbol{B}^{\mathrm{I}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)+\boldsymbol{B}^{\mathrm{R}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t)\right] \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{z}=\boldsymbol{B}^{\mathrm{T}}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{z}$。波矢 $k$ 的切向分量连续，即 $k_{0} \sin \theta=k^{\prime} \sin \gamma$。结合第四个方程，由前面两个方程可得

\begin{align*}
& A+R=E(0) \tag{1} \\
& k_{0}(R-A) \cos \theta=\mathrm{i} E^{\prime}(0) \tag{2}
\end{align*}

第三个方程给出与式 (1) 同样的结果。

相应电场为

\[
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) & = c \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{n} \\
& = \frac{\mathrm{i} \omega^{2} P_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)}}{2 \pi \varepsilon_{0} c^{2} r} \sin \theta \sin \left(\frac{k}{2} a \sin \theta \cos \varphi\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}
\end{aligned}
\]

answers:
\[
\boxed{\frac{\mathrm{i} \omega^{2} P_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)}}{2 \pi \varepsilon_{0} c^{2} r} \sin \theta \sin \left(\frac{k}{2} a \sin \theta \cos \varphi\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}}
\]

solution:
在稀薄等离子体中， $\sigma=\mathrm{i} \frac{n e^{2}}{m \omega}$. 参考题 4.21 ，可得复介电常数

\begin{equation*}
\varepsilon^{\prime}=\left(1-\frac{\omega_{\mathrm{P}}^{2}}{\omega^{2}}\right) \varepsilon_{0} \tag{13}
\end{equation*}

式中， $\omega_{\mathrm{P}}^{2}=\frac{n e^{2}}{m \varepsilon_{0}}$ 为等离子体频率. 对等离子体，可近似取 $\mu=\mu_{0}$. 代入式(2)有

$$
k^{\prime 2}=\frac{1}{c^{2}}\left(\omega^{2}-\omega_{\mathrm{P}}^{2}\right)
$$

当 $\omega_{\mathrm{P}}^{2}<\omega^{2}$ 时， $k^{\prime}$ 为实数，代入式（9）得

\begin{align*}
& E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{1+\frac{c k^{\prime}}{\omega}}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{1+\left(1-\omega_{\mathrm{P}}^{2} / \omega^{2}\right)^{1 / 2}}  \tag{14}\\
& E^{\prime \prime}=E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k z-\omega t)} e_{y} \tag{15}
\end{align*}

当 $\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}>\omega^{2}$ 时, $k^{\prime}$ 为虚数, 有

\begin{align*}
& E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{1+\mathrm{i}\left(\omega_{\mathrm{p}}^{2} / \omega^{2}-1\right)^{1 / 2}}  \tag{16}\\
& E^{\prime \prime}=E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{-k^{\prime} \mid z} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \omega t} \tag{17}
\end{align*}

对低速振动电荷，忽略磁场的作用，由题 4.21 知，在电磁波照射下，电荷的位移为

$$
x=-\frac{q \boldsymbol{E}_{0}}{m \omega^{2}} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t}
$$

故得电偶极矩为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{P}(t) &= q \boldsymbol{x} = -\frac{q^{2} \boldsymbol{E}_{0}}{m \omega^{2}} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t} \\
\ddot{\boldsymbol{P}}\left(t-\frac{r}{c}\right) &= \frac{q^{2} \boldsymbol{E}_{0}}{m} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \\
k &= \frac{\omega}{c}
\end{aligned}
$$

代入本题所给辐射场公式可得

$$
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) & =-\frac{\mu_{0} q^{2}}{4 \pi m r c} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0} \\
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) & =\frac{\mu_{0} q^{2}}{4 \pi m r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \times\left(\boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0}\right) \\
& =\frac{\mu_{0} q^{2}}{4 \pi m r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)}\left[\left(\boldsymbol{E}_{0} \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}-\boldsymbol{E}_{0}\right]
\end{aligned}
$$

answers:
\[
\boxed{\boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) =-\frac{\mu_{0} q^{2}}{4 \pi m r c} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{0}, \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) =\frac{\mu_{0} q^{2}}{4 \pi m r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)}\left[\left(\boldsymbol{E}_{0} \cdot \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}-\boldsymbol{E}_{0}\right]}
\]

problem:
考虑自由空间中下列形式的电磁波

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{E}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} kz - \mathrm{i} \omega t}, \\
& \boldsymbol{B}(x, y, z, t) = \boldsymbol{B}_{0}(x, y) \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} kz - \mathrm{i} \omega t}
\end{aligned}
$$

(d) 用中心导体上单位长度的电荷 $\lambda$ 和电流 $I$ 表示 $\boldsymbol{E}$ 和 $\boldsymbol{B}$。

solution:
解 在导体中， $\boldsymbol{j}=\sigma \boldsymbol{E}, \rho=0$，故麦克斯韦方程组为

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}=-\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{B}}{\partial t}, \quad \nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}=\frac{\partial \boldsymbol{D}}{\partial t}+\boldsymbol{j} \\
& \nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{D}=\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}=0 \\
& \boldsymbol{D}=\varepsilon \boldsymbol{E}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}=\mu \boldsymbol{H}
\end{aligned}
$$

对于定态电磁波

$$
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)=\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)=\boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t}
$$

由麦克斯韦方程组可得

\begin{gather*}
\left\{\begin{array}{l}
\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=\mathrm{i} \omega \mu \boldsymbol{H}(\boldsymbol{x}) \\
\nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}(\boldsymbol{x})=-\mathrm{i} \omega \varepsilon \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})+\sigma \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x}) \\
\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{x})=0
\end{array}\right.  \tag{1}\\
\begin{aligned}
\nabla \times(\nabla \times \boldsymbol{E})=\nabla(\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{E})-\nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E}=-\nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E} \\
\quad=\mathrm{i} \omega \mu \nabla \times \boldsymbol{H}=\left(\omega^{2} \varepsilon \mu+\mathrm{i} \omega \mu \sigma\right) \boldsymbol{E}
\end{aligned}
\end{gather*}

令

\begin{equation*}
k^{\prime 2}=\omega^{2} \mu \varepsilon^{\prime}, \quad \varepsilon^{\prime}=\varepsilon+\mathrm{i} \frac{\sigma}{\omega} \tag{2}
\end{equation*}

则

\begin{equation*}
\nabla^{2} \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})+k^{\prime 2} \boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=0 \tag{3}
\end{equation*}

这是亥姆霍兹方程，平面波是其一种特解。即

$$
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{x})=\boldsymbol{E}_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{k}^{\prime} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}}
$$

$\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}$ 为复波矢量. 令 $\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}=\boldsymbol{\beta}+\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{\alpha}$，则有

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \beta^{2}-\alpha^{2}=\omega^{2} \mu \varepsilon \\
& \boldsymbol{\beta} \cdot \boldsymbol{\alpha}=\frac{1}{2} \omega \mu \sigma
\end{aligned}
$$

对本题，入射波 $E=E_{y 0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k z-\omega t)}$，且

$$
\boldsymbol{k}=k \boldsymbol{e}_{z}, \quad \boldsymbol{E}_{0}=\boldsymbol{E}_{y 0} \boldsymbol{e}_{y}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}_{0}=\boldsymbol{B}_{x 0} \boldsymbol{e}_{x}
$$

设在半无限介质中的透射波为 $\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime \prime} 、 \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime \prime}$，有

$$
\boldsymbol{E}^{\prime \prime}=\boldsymbol{E}_{0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\left(k^{\prime} \cdot z-\omega t\right)}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}^{\prime \prime}=\boldsymbol{B}_{0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\left(k^{\prime} \cdot z-\omega t\right)}
$$

在分界面上，为保证面上各点的边值关系都成立，必须要求

$$
\boldsymbol{k} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}=\left.\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime} \cdot \boldsymbol{x}\right|_{z=0}
$$

从而可得

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \alpha_{x}=\alpha_{y}=\beta_{x}=\beta_{y}=0 \\
& \boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}=k^{\prime} \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \\
& k^{\prime}=\beta+\mathrm{i} \alpha
\end{aligned}
$$

$\beta$ 、 $\alpha$ 满足联立方程

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \beta^{2}-\alpha^{2}=\omega^{2} \mu \varepsilon \\
& \beta \alpha=\frac{1}{2} \omega \mu \sigma
\end{aligned}
$$

其解为

\begin{align*}
& \beta=\omega \sqrt{\mu \varepsilon}\left[\frac{1}{2}\left(1+\sqrt{1+\frac{\sigma^{2}}{\varepsilon^{2} \omega^{2}}}\right)\right]^{1 / 2}  \tag{4}\\
& \alpha=\omega \sqrt{\mu \varepsilon}\left[\frac{1}{2}\left(-1+\sqrt{1+\frac{\sigma^{2}}{\varepsilon^{2} \omega^{2}}}\right)\right]^{1 / 2} \tag{5}
\end{align*}

下面用边值关系求透射波的振幅。设反射波的振幅为 $\boldsymbol{E}_{0}^{\prime} 、 \boldsymbol{H}_{0}^{\prime}$ ，由平面波的横波性及在分界面上 $\boldsymbol{E}$ 的法向连续性及 $\boldsymbol{H}$ 的切向连续性，首先可知反射波与折射波的电场只有 $y$ 分量，磁场只有 $x$ 分量，并且满足

\begin{align*}
& E_{y 0}+E_{y 0}^{\prime}=E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}  \tag{6}\\
& E_{x 0}+E_{x 0}^{\prime}=E_{x 0}^{\prime \prime} \tag{7}
\end{align*}

对入射波与反射波 $H_{x 0}=\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon_{0}}{\mu_{0}}} E_{y 0}, H_{x 0}^{\prime}=\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon_{0}}{\mu_{0}}} E_{y 0}^{\prime}$ 。并由式(1)得 $H_{x 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{k^{\prime}}{\omega \mu} E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}$ ，从而可把式（7）化成

\begin{equation*}
\sqrt{\frac{\varepsilon_{0}}{\mu_{0}}}\left(E_{y 0}-E_{y 0}^{\prime}\right)=\frac{k^{\prime}}{\omega \mu} E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime} \tag{8}
\end{equation*}

式(6)与式(8)联立，解得

\begin{equation*}
E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{1+\sqrt{\frac{\mu_{0}}{\varepsilon_{0}}} \cdot \frac{k^{\prime}}{\omega \mu}} \tag{9}
\end{equation*}

当 $\sigma$ 很大且为实数， $\omega$ 是低频时，有

$$
\frac{\sigma}{\varepsilon \omega} \gg 1, \quad \sqrt{1+\frac{\sigma^{2}}{\varepsilon^{2} \omega^{2}}} \pm 1 \approx \frac{\sigma}{\varepsilon \omega}
$$

所以

\begin{equation*}
\beta=\alpha \approx \sqrt{\frac{\omega \mu \sigma}{2}} \tag{10}
\end{equation*}

故

\begin{align*}
& k^{\prime}=\sqrt{\frac{\omega \mu \sigma}{2}}(1+\mathrm{i}) \\
& E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime}=\frac{2 E_{y 0}}{\left(1+\sqrt{\frac{\mu_{0} \sigma}{2 \varepsilon_{0} \omega \mu}}+\mathrm{i} \sqrt{\frac{\mu_{0} \sigma}{2 \varepsilon_{0} \omega \mu}}\right)} \tag{11}
\end{align*}

即在金属中的电场为

\begin{equation*}
E^{\prime \prime}=E_{y 0}^{\prime \prime} \mathrm{e}^{-\alpha z} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(\beta z-\omega t)} e_{y} \tag{12}
\end{equation*}

能流密度

$$
\begin{aligned}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} & =\frac{1}{2 \mu_{0}} \text{Re}\left(\boldsymbol{E}^{\star} \times \boldsymbol{B}\right) \\
& =\frac{(\varepsilon-\varepsilon_{0}) a^{6} \omega^{4}}{2 \mu_{0}(\varepsilon+2 \varepsilon_{0})^{2} c^{5}} \cdot \frac{E_{0}^{2} \sin^2 \theta}{R^{2}} \boldsymbol{e}_{R}
\end{aligned}
$$

由此得出散射电磁波沿介质球的法向传播，散射电场的偏振在 $\boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}$，磁场在 $\boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi}$ 方向。

因为 $|\boldsymbol{r}| \gg \lambda \gg z_{0}$, 故可用多极展开法求电磁场。由于自有场与 $\frac{1}{r^{2}}$ 成比例，我们忽略不计，只求与 $\frac{1}{r}$ 成比例的辐射场。在题图 5.17 中，电偶极矩 $\boldsymbol{P} = \left(q z_{1} + q z_{2}\right) \boldsymbol{e}_{z} = 0$。电四极矩

$$
\overrightarrow{\boldsymbol{D}} = 6 q z_{0}^{2} \sin^{2} \omega t \boldsymbol{e}_{z}
$$

令

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{D} = \boldsymbol{n} \cdot \boldsymbol{D} = \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}} \cdot \boldsymbol{D} = 6 q z_{0}^{2} \cos \theta \sin^{2} \omega t \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \\
& \dot{\boldsymbol{D}} = 6 q z_{0}^{2} \omega \cos \theta \sin 2 \omega t \boldsymbol{e}_{z}
\end{aligned}
$$

此电荷系统在 $\boldsymbol{r}$ 处产生的矢势为

$$
\boldsymbol{A}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = -\frac{\mathrm{i} k \mu_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k r}}{24 \pi r} \dot{\boldsymbol{D}}
$$

辐射场为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{B}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) & = \mathrm{i} k \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{A} = \frac{k^{2} \mu_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k r}}{24 \pi r} \cdot 6 q z_{0}^{2} \omega \cos \theta \sin 2 \omega t \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{e}_{z} \\
& = -\frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{3} q z_{0}^{2} \sin \theta \cos \theta}{4 \pi c^{2} r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k r} \sin 2 \omega t \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi} \\
\boldsymbol{E}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) & = c \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{n} = -\frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{3} q z_{0}^{2} \sin \theta \cos \theta}{4 \pi c r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k r} \sin 2 \omega t \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}
\end{aligned}
$$

当 $\phi_{0}=\frac{\pi}{2}$ 时, 有

$$
\begin{align*}
\boldsymbol{B} & =-\frac{\omega^{2} p_{0}}{4 \pi \varepsilon_{0} c^{3} r} e^{\mathrm{i} k r}\left(\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}-\cos \theta \boldsymbol{e}_{\phi}\right) e^{-\mathrm{i}(\omega t-\phi)}, \tag{6} \\
\boldsymbol{E} & =\frac{\omega^{2} p_{0}}{4 \pi \varepsilon_{0} c^{3} r} e^{\mathrm{i} k r}\left(\cos \theta \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta}+\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{e}_{\phi}\right) e^{-\mathrm{i}(\omega t-\phi)}. \tag{7}
\end{align*}
$$

如图4.12，入射偏振波为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}_{1} = E_{10} e^{i(k_{1} x - \omega t)}, \quad \boldsymbol{B}_{1} = B_{10} e^{i(k_{1} x - \omega t)} \\
& B_{10} = n E_{10}, \quad k_{1} = \frac{\omega}{c} n
\end{aligned}
\]

反射波为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}_{2} = E_{20} e^{-i(k_{2} x + \omega t)} \\
& \boldsymbol{B}_{2} = B_{20} e^{-i(k_{2} x + \omega t)} \\
& B_{20} = n E_{20}, \quad k_{2} = \frac{\omega}{c} n
\end{aligned}
\]

透射波为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{E}_{3} = E_{30} e^{i(k_{3} x - \omega t)} \\
& \boldsymbol{B}_{3} = B_{30} e^{i(k_{3} x - \omega t)} \\
& B_{30} = n_{2} E_{30}, \quad k_{3} = \frac{\omega}{c} n_{2}
\end{aligned}
\]

在边界面处，\(x=0\), 三波频率 \(\omega\) 相同，边界关系为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{n} \times (\boldsymbol{E}_{10} + \boldsymbol{E}_{20}) = \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{E}_{30}, \quad \boldsymbol{E} \text{ 的切向分量连续} \\
& \boldsymbol{n} \times (\boldsymbol{B}_{10} + \boldsymbol{B}_{20}) = \boldsymbol{n} \times \frac{\boldsymbol{B}_{30}}{\mu} \approx \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{B}_{30}, \quad \text{磁场的切向分量连续}
\end{aligned}
\]

即为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& E_{10} - E_{20} = E_{30} \\
& B_{10} + B_{20} = B_{30}
\end{aligned}
\]

后一式可化为

\[
E_{10} + E_{20} = \frac{n_{2}}{n} E_{30}
\]

由此可解出

\[
\begin{aligned}
& E_{20} = \frac{n_{2} - n}{n_{2} + n} E_{10} = \frac{i n \rho}{2n + i n \rho} E_{10} = \frac{\rho}{\sqrt{\rho^{2} + 4}} e^{i\varphi} E_{10} \\
& \tan \varphi = \frac{2}{\rho}
\end{aligned}
\]

即反射波电矢量振幅相对入射波的相移为

\[
\varphi' = \arctan \frac{2}{\rho}
\]

取圆环中心为原点，设空间点位置矢量为 \(\boldsymbol{r}(r, \theta, \varphi)\)，当 \( r \rightarrow \infty \) 时，该点的矢势为

\[
\boldsymbol{A}(\boldsymbol{r}, t) = \frac{i k \mu_{0} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k r}}{4 \pi r} \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{m}
\]

式中，\(\boldsymbol{n} = \boldsymbol{e}_{\mathrm{r}}, k = \frac{\omega}{c} \)，取复数形式的磁偶极矩

\[
\boldsymbol{m} = \pi a^{2} i_{0} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \omega t} \boldsymbol{e}_{z}
\]

真实值理解为其实部，则得矢势公式为

\[
\boldsymbol{A}(r, t) = -i \frac{\mu_{0} \omega i_{0} a^{2} \sin \theta}{4 c r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi}
\]

其相应的辐射电磁场为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \boldsymbol{B} = \nabla \times \boldsymbol{A} = i k \boldsymbol{n} \times \boldsymbol{A} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{2} i_{0} a^{2} \sin \theta}{4 c^{2} r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\theta} \\
& \boldsymbol{E} = c \boldsymbol{B} \times \boldsymbol{n} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{2} i_{0} a^{2} \sin \theta}{4 c r} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}(k r-\omega t)} \boldsymbol{e}_{\varphi}
\end{aligned}
\]

平均能流密度为

\[
\begin{aligned}
\overline{\boldsymbol{S}} & = \frac{1}{2} \operatorname{Re}\left\{\boldsymbol{E}^{*} \times \boldsymbol{H}\right\} = \frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}} \operatorname{Re}\left\{\left(\boldsymbol{B}^{*} \times \boldsymbol{n}\right) \times \boldsymbol{B}\right\} \\
& = \frac{c}{2 \mu_{0}}|\boldsymbol{B}|^{2} \boldsymbol{n} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{4} i_{0}^{2} a^{4}}{32 c^{3} r^{2}} \sin^{2} \theta \boldsymbol{n}
\end{aligned}
\]

设 \( P \) 为平均辐射功率，辐射角分布为

\[
\frac{\mathrm{d} P}{\mathrm{~d} \Omega} = S r^{2} = \frac{\mu_{0} \omega^{4} a^{4} i_{0}^{2}}{32 c^{3}} \sin^{2} \theta
\]
